    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到 <i>Thronefall</i>、<i>SNKRX</i> 和 <i>Warcraft 3</i> 等游戏的启发，Wool at the Gates 将极简战术塔防与类自走棋的深度职业协同机制和 MOBA 式英雄动作相结合，带来战略基地建设与史诗战斗交替进行的刺激游戏循环。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220780/extras/c6d0e5918ba28911317019c283f688b0.poster.avif?t=1763581349\" width=1170 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220780/extras/c6d0e5918ba28911317019c283f688b0.webm?t=1763581349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220780/extras/c6d0e5918ba28911317019c283f688b0.mp4?t=1763581349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在越来越具挑战性的回合中防御入侵的羊群，每个回合都先有战术建造阶段，然后是史诗战斗。做出战略决策，权衡各种建筑的利弊，深入研究派系天赋树并最大化类自走棋职业协同机制。观看你精心设计的协同在你的防御与羊群之间的全面混战中爆发，你的英雄作为终极指挥官带领冲锋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220780/extras/203ba2f9e8fa13a0d553186c5f33366a.poster.avif?t=1763581349\" width=1170 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220780/extras/203ba2f9e8fa13a0d553186c5f33366a.webm?t=1763581349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220780/extras/203ba2f9e8fa13a0d553186c5f33366a.mp4?t=1763581349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基地建设：</strong> 建造并升级塔、墙和资源生成建筑来抵御羊群——有限的建造槽使每一次选择都至关重要</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回合制关卡：</strong> 在下一波开始前充分规划并部署部队，突破一系列难度递增的回合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>类自走棋协同：</strong> 协调城市防御以解锁强力职业加成，并选择你的玩法风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>派系天赋树：</strong> 建造人类、兽人或精灵建筑以解锁每个派系的独特天赋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>爽快战斗：</strong> 在释放英雄技能、优化部署并实时指挥部队的非凡行动中抵御狼羊之势</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重玩价值：</strong> 在更高难度重玩关卡，完成挑战以获得奖励，并在无尽模式中检验你的防御</p></li></ul>",
